name: Tim the Bee
description:
This is my pet radioactive bumblebee. He loves uranium honey that's only produced by Alia flowers, a plant that only grows in the deep forests of Planet Helix. His name is Tim :) 

All photography🖼️ was produced and edited by 🔥Dennis Sarovski🔥, Poem is by my Wife :)
